{"error":0,"message":"","data":[{"show_ID":"1794","airdate":"1472061600","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Bozzy and the Bint","showname":"BBKB","blurb":"It's the Taint of the Week\u2122 again, so it's time for Boz to utter complete bollocks in between your requests. Thankfully, Kate is here to translate some of it into English. All aboard the Train-Wreck, WOO WOOH!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Bozzy and the Bint<\/big><\/strong><br \/>BBKB","nice_airdate":"Wednesday 24th August, 2016<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1796","airdate":"1472148000","name_switch":"off","DJ":"KraxxUltima","showname":"The Ultimate Crack","blurb":"Welcome back to yet another of those things eh. If you have the need for more C64 and Amiga tunes played whilst our madman (the DJ) tries to entertain you during the dying summer days, then tune in =)  and have fun.","nice_showname":"<strong><big>KraxxUltima<\/big><\/strong><br \/>The Ultimate Crack","nice_airdate":"Thursday 25th August, 2016<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"},{"show_ID":"1795","airdate":"1472407200","name_switch":"off","DJ":"Gazoo","showname":"PMPVsGermany","blurb":"Given that this will, for foreseeable future, be my very last show in Germany - it feels fitting to entitle it so. But the topic's of the show will actually revolve quite little around my migratory move. There are far more interesting topics on the horizon if you ask me.\n\nWell... Maybe I'll talk a tiny bit about moving.\n\nTopics for tonight:\n\n- The end of Gawker and associated media\/journalistic\/stuff\n- Penny Auctions (are the tool of the devil)\n- Migrating\/Moving 20,000 km\n- Possibly an amazingly unique and new feature in PlanMixPlay\n\nStay Frosty!","nice_showname":"<strong><big>Gazoo<\/big><\/strong><br \/>PMPVsGermany","nice_airdate":"Sunday 28th August, 2016<br \/>at 20:00 USRT"}]}